StepBro.Core.Parser.Grammar.StepBroBaseVisitor< Result > Class Template Reference

This class provides an empty implementation of IStepBroVisitor<Result>, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods. More...

Detailed Description

This class provides an empty implementation of IStepBroVisitor<Result>, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.

Template Parameters
ResultThe return type of the visit operation.
